<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11510>
    dc:description "Figures 15 - 25. Orientopius europaeus sp. n., female, holotype. 15 wings 16 mesosoma dorsal 17 mesosoma lateral 18 metasoma dorsal 19 ovipositor sheath lateral 20 head anterior 21 head dorsal 22 malar space 23 base of antenna 24 apex of antenna 25 hind leg." ;
